# Captured trace corpora — ship the 4 demos that cover the named workflow areas
# (invoices, contracts, reports*, plus the loan_calculator generalization headline);
# everything else stays local (reviewer regenerates via `python scripts/capture_traces.py`).
# *release_notes_compiler stands in for the "reports" area + adds the D003+D006+D008 demo.
traces/*
!traces/invoice_validator/
!traces/loan_calculator/
!traces/release_notes_compiler/
!traces/contract_redline_reviewer/

# Per-run optimizer outputs (auto-generated on every run)
